title: Protocol maintenance finalization
body:
Protocol maintenance finalization, turn on TokenSpender module back to work on updated contracts

This is last step of previously passed proposal
https://signal.opium.network/#/proposal/QmQKTMY3Wbm8dcmAL63EQmkiPPbtcqUycMoVC981aiLzbn

The poposal is setting the TokenSpender's whitelist to an array with updated contracts

Updated contracts are opensourced and validated, please double check here:
https://etherscan.io/address/0xd60f0a53c7e97f78fe4ac9013f5749920c601494
https://etherscan.io/address/0x09a439c50465e447cb1a662da536f23a7e39374e

Updates were discussed in the global contributors call and approved by auditors

This proposal will enable creation of new transactions
author: 0x84E94F8032b3F9fEc34EE05F192Ad57003337988
